Inhibition of FAK (unknown origin) assembly after 20 mins by turbidimetric method
Binding affinity to FAK kinase (unknown origin) by surface plasmon resonance assay
Inhibition of FAK (unknown origin) at 10 uM by [33P]-ATP radiometric assay
Inhibition of FAK (unknown origin) at 10 uM after 120 mins P33 radiolabeled kinase activity assay
Inhibition of PTK2 (unknown origin) at 500 nM
Inhibition of FAK at 10 uM by HTRF assay relative to control
